<p>Restoring lost contacts, signing onto websites with Facebook, cloning drives, troubleshooting external enclosures and learning about the behind-the-scenes of junk mail filtering are just&nbsp;<em>some</em>&nbsp;of the topics discussed by your two favorite geeks today. Download and enjoy!</p>
